      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，我先确认一下结构。起始点用Groupware_KanbanBoard作为入口，然后连接到EmptyLot。车辆停入时从EmptyLot到PartiallyFull，再停满到Full。移除车辆时反向流转，对吗？",
