        "Groupware_KanbanBoard",
        "EmptyLot",
        "PartiallyFull",
        "Full",
        "Park vehicle",
        "Remove vehicle"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，但PartiallyFull的定义要写清楚——是\"Some slots occupied\"，Full则是\"All slots occupied\"，EmptyLot标注\"No vehicles parked\"。另外维护模式的触发条件统一叫\"Enter maintenance mode\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PartiallyFull",
        "Full",
        "EmptyLot",
        "Maintenance",
        "Enter maintenance mode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已添加三个状态到Maintenance的转移，标注都是Enter maintenance mode。现在处理维护后的恢复：从Maintenance可以直接Reset lot回到EmptyLot，或者Restore previous state回到PartiallyFull。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Maintenance",
        "EmptyLot",
        "PartiallyFull",
        "Reset lot",
        "Restore previous state"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，Restore previous state这里有问题——如果维护前是Full状态，恢复后也应该能回到Full，而不仅是PartiallyFull。我需要这个流转能覆盖所有前置状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Maintenance",
        "Full",
        "PartiallyFull",
        "Restore previous state"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "理解了，但Mermaid状态图里一个转移只能指向一个目标状态。我建议这样处理：Maintenance到PartiallyFull的Restore previous state作为通用恢复路径，因为无论之前是Full还是PartiallyFull，恢复后都需要重新检测实际占用情况，逻辑上都会先进入PartiallyFull再判断是否继续填满。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Maintenance",
        "PartiallyFull",
        "Restore previous state"
